{"tid":1077510,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你近況好嗎","createTime":"2019-03-25T15:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T16:25:19.000Z","uid":244641,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4f425112f8efe01211ef0615fb307db300a2cbcf","tid":1077510,"uid":244641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:28:53.000Z","msg":"好想搵個地方呻啊啊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢段時間我以為可以放低你，但其實我根本就唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />身邊既朋友都以為我已經冇事，成日仲on99咁大笑，佢地都安慰咗我好多次，唔想再打擾佢地。<br />\n<br />\n我已經嘗試過好多方法去忘記你，但最後我都係會掛住你。<br />\n我試過寫日記，不過我寫完幾隻字已經喊到隻手會震 ，字都寫唔到。旅行個陣好想同你分享每一個風景，發生既特別事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無奈我唔可以，亦冇資格<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每次諗到你同第二個男仔可能曖昧緊，傾電話，好似之前對我咁，我個心痛好似俾人扔去碎紙機，好難受<br />\n<br />\n有幾次我真係痛到呼吸唔到，有冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我打開個通話紀錄全部都係你個名，好想再同你傾電話，好想聽到你把聲啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3528a20b434725ae13938f5a9b0efab45ef5b5a9","tid":1077510,"uid":70979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce062dcc636a5e72793badd240b98a23e13a36f1","tid":1077510,"uid":244641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3528a20b434725ae13938f5a9b0efab45ef5b5a9","tid":1077510,"uid":70979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score